How to run the project?

1. create a .env file containing these environment variables:
    1. MONGO_URL = <-- your bearer token that links to your mongodb server -->
    2. TWITTER_USERNAME = <-- your twitter handle --> <-- @abcssdf23 -->
    3. TWITTER_PASSKEY = <-- your twitter password -->
    4. MAIL = <-- your email linked to your twitter -->

2. install all the modules necessary. you will find the modules list in "requirement.txt".

3. everything inter linked to the page.py file which has the Streamlit GUI code.
   - using command "streamlit run page.py" in the command line interface will start the application.
